title: Alaska Delegation Continues to Promote Strategic Buildup of Interior Alaska (Don Young)
text: ( Source : Don Young ) WASHINGTON, DC - The Alaska Congressional Delegation today welcomed news from the Missile Defense Agency that they have awarded a $784,289, 883 contract to Lockheed Martin to build the Long Range Discrimination Radar
